Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.34,0:01:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公國之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球聯邦政府發起了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.82,0:01:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開始一個月的戰鬥里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.94,0:01:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍有半數以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.82,0:01:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們對於自己的行為產生了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.55,0:02:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『伊榭蓮娜的悲戀』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在月球的另一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.33,0:02:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浮游著多個太空都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用獨裁手段支配地球的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.32,0:02:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩比家支配的宇宙都市國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.24,0:02:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這些漂流宇宙的圓筒建築物內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.92,0:02:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有著人類生存的空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.92,0:02:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個都市的直徑有6公里闊及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.72,0:02:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長30公里以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面有著和自然一樣的環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.37,0:02:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使人可以像在地球般地生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.01,0:03:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION國的宇宙攻擊軍司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德茲爾中將正從前線趕回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和半年前一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒有加強工事建設
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.11,0:03:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙殖民地是利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離心力來製造重心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們在裏面的大地生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是ZION公國的首都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲姆市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不可讓卡爾瑪白白犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這會影響我們薩比家的聲譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基連
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.73,0:04:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在已經覺得很傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.16,0:04:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報告陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德茲爾中將及基西莉亞少將已從前線趕回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他們入來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.87,0:04:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們倆都回來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！父王！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王，別太傷心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.83,0:04:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪作夢也想不到聯邦軍的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會打敗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.89,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在我還未可接受他的死訊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只在憶念卡爾瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不可戰勝的，德茲爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪很聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連我也很佩服他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且將來也會勝過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是五星上將的好人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德茲爾說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該以沉重心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.28,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來追掉卡爾瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害你久等了，依榭蓮娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭蓮娜小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前日的晚會上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已見過你動人丰姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.48,0:05:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有將校都異口同聲地讚你美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏就是上校的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳現在一定是很傷心的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們一定會為上校報仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭蓮娜小姐，我們一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅達中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.41,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.60,0:06:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我乘上卡烏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭蓮娜小姐，妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很憎恨害死卡爾瑪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是只能開一槍也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一定要報這個仇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅達中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說也還未是時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了這裏已經和到達了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍會來接我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很心急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.24,0:06:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想第一個落地面呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一股很強大的氣流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.98,0:07:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是風眼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在本艦進入亂氣流內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將有持續的震盪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為裏面有保險制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不能投出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你是機械天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.86,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以兩個一起用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是同一樣的東西呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,12號地點發現敵軍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有3台卡烏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,探測器顯示是卡烏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一共3台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修理好GUNDAM了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時可以出動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎好像故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，需要緊急降落嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只差一點便到我軍範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許有援軍來呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先想辦法到聯邦軍制空圈內較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出去反會被氣流捲走的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我認為會有利才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，我們一次過盡量跳過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試一試吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標機動戰士出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.93,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是他殺死了卡爾瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.00,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何，我也會助你復仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭蓮娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開炮，開炮，射他下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，小心別接近炮門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找死的便來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2號機去支援3號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們太可惡了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們還有戰機嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很對不起，在多次作戰後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.25,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以用的都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.39,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是夏亞少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來助你一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞，我是卡爾瑪上校直屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫羅達中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰也好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起瞄準控制室攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制室？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.87,0:10:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腹部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM心臟部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先去攻擊木馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要集中破壞便成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使卡爾瑪戰死的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表示對薩比家的忠誠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何一方面也不會有損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍有電報來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對White Base的支持仍在爭議中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不會有援軍來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連瑪吉路達中尉作為中間人而來一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也引起非議...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他們根本想我們去送死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還未讀完全封電報呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們準備收留難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請向S109
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和N23地點方面航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，轉向1.5方向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.31,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敵軍從前方來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了，保險擎壞了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！左後方被擊中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方向舵也受損了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒法控制方向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急降落，大家扶隱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有安全帶的請扣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,著陸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有好方法可以奪取母艦到手嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，妳做得相當好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非我的駕駛術了得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是White Base性能出色罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳太謙了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，妳沒受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以幫我看看難民的情況嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時還可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.68,0:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,落到地面再算吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不可讓兇手走脫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定...一定要殺死他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我將引擎部份做好應急處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以支持下去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.90,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好極！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.41,0:14:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎部份可以用了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有百分之25左右動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.91,0:14:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉強可以應付！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想不到母艦如此捱得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！我們要快離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若再受襲的話便不能再動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不和阿姆羅和良聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未聯絡到他們嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍未收到他們的報告呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長 隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已有數名難民逃到外面去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.94,0:15:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能再忍受下去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.61,0:15:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！別去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.91,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面很危險的 別去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.05,0:15:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你回來，很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人可能就在附近的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION軍想要的只是母艦和GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我們根本就沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.96,0:15:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留在母艦才危險呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快給我們走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是沙漠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們走不掉的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 他是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.03,0:16:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪的追悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是我們一家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何不妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王，現在是戰爭之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.95,0:16:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為讓國民統一，情緒高漲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.45,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該用國葬方法來追悼才適合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.12,0:16:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次卡爾瑪的死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非單就他一人的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是ZION全國的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也贊成大哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要先處分夏亞才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不能盡責保護卡爾瑪的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.50,0:16:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處罰他可給人民一個警惕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些事應該在你權力範圍內做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.21,0:17:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在最重要的是舉行儀式，父王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪一直在人民心目中很有人緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以透過用國葬的儀式來追悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.06,0:17:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以激起人民對聯邦的怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於夏亞的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.74,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德茲爾你將他降職處分吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王，你是ZION的國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請快指示應該怎樣處理...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，掩護我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！大家集中火力攻擊機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再繼續加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.36,0:18:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把機動戰士毀滅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盾抵擋不住了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.27,0:18:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅達中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的手不行了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.57,0:19:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我來駕駛吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭蓮娜小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.94,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪的仇便報不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.49,0:19:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.49,0:19:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要為卡爾瑪報仇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟！不知那裏壞了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！你沒受傷吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.56,0:20:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，看來GUNDAM故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出去看看情況！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡烏上可能有士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.10,0:20:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.84,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅達中尉...中尉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你就是殺卡爾瑪的兇手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是...兇手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.92,0:21:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別人是靠不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.16,0:21:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杜力，有人問起我的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.33,0:21:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便說計算機系統繞壞了就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是救援隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.65,0:22:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.92,0:22:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說我是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.78,0:23:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅疲倦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.67,0:23:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是新的敵人蘭巴·拉爾降臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.75,0:23:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型機動戰士強大的破壞力玩弄著GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而此時聽到ZION萬歲的呼喊聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.58,0:23:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.21,0:23:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『ZION的威脅』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.99,0:23:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎？

